Friends and family are celebrating the life of veteran journalist and political analyst Karima Brown. Courtesy #DStv403 JOHANNESBURG - Friends and family are celebrating the life of veteran journalist and political analyst Karima Brown. Brown passed away from COVID-19 related complications last week. WATCH: Memorial service of the late Karima Brown Her friends and family remembered her life during a memorial service at the Sacred Heart College in Johannesburg. eNCA’s Aviwe Mtila shares more details in the video above.